Package org.neo4j.bolt.packstream

Class ChunkedOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.bolt.packstream.ChunkedOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, PackOutput
    public class ChunkedOutput
extends Object
implements PackOutput
    A target output for PackStream which breaks the data into a continuous stream of chunks before pushing them into a netty channel.
